'''Gulden''' is a medic who helped treat [[Molly]] on her way to the hospital.

==History==
===Molly===
While Ben was driving [[Molly]] to the hospital, Gulden was treating her in the back and gave Ben reports of her status along the way. ''("[[No Recovery]]")''

===Sean===
Jack asked Gulden where [[Sean (Lost and Found)|Sean]] was and Gulden told him that they tried to treat him, but he left as soon as Jack did. ''("[[Lost and Found]]")''

==Career==
He is a paramedic with the Seattle Fire Department.
